originalText.text:
I was contact by this staffing agency who said they had a role open for me and wanted to screen my background.  When I asked to see a job description to see if I fit the role, they told me they didn't establish trust to reveal this information.  I did not ask for the company.

Coming from an executive recruiter background, the recruiter was feeding me all the standard lines to have me come in and meet with them to just be a candidate in the system for future use. They continuously say they have all these years of experience but something does not feel right.  The recruiter who contacted me was not even listed on their website as part of the recruitment team.
